source.name: Hospital Inpatient Discharges by DRG, Northwest, FY2011
source.description: This table shows the low, high, and average percents of discharges related to a referenced DRG (diagnosis-related group) as a share of the total discharges from the top 100 common DRGs for hospitals in the Northwest region (Alaska, Idaho, Oregon, and Washington). The source of data for this table is FY2011 hospital charges file provided by the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services (CMS).
